# Editor Module

## Overview

AutoDown Editor provides WYSIWYG block-based editing with Markdown/AutoDown serialization for Wiki and Spec content

## Goals

- **G1** — AutoDown Editor provides WYSIWYG block-based editing with Markdown/AutoDown serialization for Wiki and Spec content
- **G2** — Phase 1 — Markdown WYSIWYG Editor
- **G3** — Phase 2 — AutoDown Extensions
- **G4** — Phase 3 — Advanced Editing Features

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — AutoDown Editor — Tiptap-Based WYSIWYG Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — AutoDown Editor — Block-Based WYSIWYG with Markdown/AutoDown Serialization

## Module Dependencies

Depends on: [wiki](wiki/module.ad)

